491
00:38:22,241 --> 00:38:23,265
他……
{\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fscy70\1c&H00FFFF&}He's...{\r}

492
00:38:23,909 --> 00:38:26,503
……是個非常特別的同伴,魯珀特
{\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fscy70\1c&H00FFFF&}...a very extraordinary fellow, Rupert.{\r}

493
00:38:27,748 --> 00:38:29,375
他可以說是……
{\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fscy70\1c&H00FFFF&}He's a sort of...{\r}

494
00:38:29,583 --> 00:38:32,040
